item.title: Friedrich Ebert Stiftung
item.description: FES Uzbekistan was founded in 1997. The foundation’s mission in the country is stated as promoting ideas of inclusive society and contributing to the development of just economic and social politics, as well as supporting civil society, labor unions, and gender equality.
